     HOW TO PLAY

          Well, it is easy. Move your Mousepointer to the box you
          want to move. Then press the RIGHT Mousebutton to move
          Box to right, and LEFT Mousebutton to move Box to the
          left. 

          If there is free space under the box, the box falls automagically 
          to the bottom. 
          
          If it find any neighbour, (Left, right or below)
          having same type then himself, these two (three) boxes disappears. 
          It could be possible, that three boxes at the time
          may disappear ! Say the fallig box finds two (three ?) neighbours at
          the time ! This is important !

          On the right side you see a list of each type of box in
          the game. So there you can look, if there are any triples
          of boxes (Odd Number).

          For the best strategy, you must improve yourself.
          Use unmatching pieces to move other pieces to left,
          right at higher places...
          Before starting a level, look at the list, to detect any
          odd-numbers, look for traps or holes.


